Scotland is without a doubt your home and we would love to continue counting on you.”
Christion Abercrombie is undergoing emergency surgery after a head injury
Tennessee State Tigers player Christion Abercrombie was surgically emergency after suffering a head injury on Saturday, when they lost 31-27 to Vanderbilt Commodores, Tennessee’s Mike Organ reported.
