Both coaches and medical staff administered oxygen to Abercrombie on the band line before placing him on a stretcher and taking him for in-depth examination.
A Tennessee State staffer told Chris Harris of WSMV in Nashville, Tennessee, that Abercrombie had left the operation at Vanderbilt Medical Center.
